The paper deals with inferring spatial-temporal properties from data, which is a common problem in machine learning and artificial intelligence. The use cases mentioned in the abstract, such as additive manufacturing systems and swarm robotic systems, suggest that the paper could fall under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), robotics (cs.RO), systems and control (cs.SY), and software engineering (cs.SE). However, since the paper focuses on developing a logic-based approach for inferring properties from graph data, it is most likely to be classified under cs.LG (Machine Learning).
